ly in a physical sense, but also in the metaphorical sense of ›exile‹ implying foreignness, exclusion, and marginalization.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Jan 2023) 4aBody. 4aDisplacement. 4aExile. 4aFemale Dancer. 4aGender. 4aIran. 4aMigration. 4aTransformation. 4aUSA. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Dance / General.2bisacsh  aBody.  aDisplacement.  aExile.  aFemale Dancer.  aGender.  aIran.  aMigration.  aTransformation.  aUSA.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2022z9783110992809oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2022 Englishz978311099281608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2022z9783111025094oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2022z97831107685100 cprintz978383766080740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839460801?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839460801423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839460801/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076851-0  transcript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099281-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishb2022  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPD